  33,57,Iste those oppose GOD Jeho posol GOD afflicts them curse v this zivot do Hereafter He chystat them shameful retribution
  33,58,Those persecute verit clovek verit zensky nie robit anything zlo committed nie iba falsehood i gross zhresit
